<node id="&lt;hyperedge&gt;&quot;If after we have waived at least one premium under this provision, the insured person recovers, but within 6 months again becomes totally disabled from the same or a related cause, we will consider the subsequent period of total disability to be a continuation of the former period.&quot;">
