<node id="&quot;POLICY&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"DOCUMENT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A document outlining the terms and conditions of the insurance coverage."&lt;SEP&gt;"A policy contract is a formal agreement that, along with application materials and evidence of insurability, forms the full insurance contract."&lt;SEP&gt;"Policy is the document that serves as evidence of insurance coverage."&lt;SEP&gt;"The document that describes the limitations and exclusions."&lt;SEP&gt;"The insurance policy is a legal document that outlines the terms and conditions of coverage."&lt;SEP&gt;"The insurance policy that may be voided if false information is found."&lt;SEP&gt;"The official document outlining the terms, benefits, exclusions, and conditions of the TD 20-Year Term Life insurance coverage."&lt;SEP&gt;"The policy allows for voiding of coverage if information is concealed or misrepresented."&lt;SEP&gt;"The policy is a legal agreement that provides insurance coverage for a specified term, with guaranteed premiums and renewal options."&lt;SEP&gt;"The policy is referenced as the document under which beneficiary designations are made."&lt;SEP&gt;"The policy is terminated when the premium is not paid within the grace period."&lt;SEP&gt;"The policy must be drawn up in English."&lt;SEP&gt;"The policy outlines terms including benefit adjustments based on underpayment."&lt;SEP&gt;"The policy outlines the requirement for proof of claim before legal action."&lt;SEP&gt;"The policy outlines the terms, conditions, and benefits of the insurance, including the waiver of premiums during total disability."&lt;SEP&gt;"The policy will end and there will be no further renewal, indicating the termination of coverage after a certain period."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-d797d61d4936328367b970f1b1a2a94b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-32b292e542e11e187b7d8150c2a86ba7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9e48b2c7f5c340d231cab1e863dc3229&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dfd5028f0b43132db8da74961939d00d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6e3c19fad0ec74d4024195693875376d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e336bc3335eae1b8a9a02061f363f289&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9664b19d2f37c02c2b9b34d8418fd48b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-03736d1fd2c6f92ba7855518c6ef9999&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5e6240fb2796b537f797e57d0cca4a3b</data>
</node>
