  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A company specializing in life insurance products, part of the TD Insurance group."&lt;SEP&gt;"A company that offers life and health insurance products."&lt;SEP&gt;"A company that offers life insurance products and is a member of the TD Bank Group."&lt;SEP&gt;"An officer of TD Life Insurance Company must sign any waiver or change."&lt;SEP&gt;"TD Life Insurance Company is the entity issuing the policy."&lt;SEP&gt;"TD Life Insurance Company is the insurer that underwrites the TD 20-Year Term Life Insurance policy."&lt;SEP&gt;"TD Life Insurance Company is the underwriter of the insurance policy and is referred to as 'the insurer' in the policy document."&lt;SEP&gt;"TD Life Insurance Company is the underwriter of the policy and is referred to as 'the insurer' and 'we', 'us', 'our' in the policy document."&lt;SEP&gt;"The insurance company issuing the policy and managing its terms."&lt;SEP&gt;"The insurance provider that underwrites the TD 20-Year Term Life insurance policy, part of the TD Bank Group."&lt;SEP&gt;"The insurer that must receive the cancellation request."</data>
