<node id="&quot;INSURED PERSON&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d4">"The Living Benefit is paid directly to the insured person."&lt;SEP&gt;"The individual covered by the policy, whose date of birth is subject to special rules."&lt;SEP&gt;"The individual covered by the policy, whose disability triggers the benefit."&lt;SEP&gt;"The individual covered by the policy; must be alive to qualify for reinstatement."&lt;SEP&gt;"The individual whose life is covered by the policy; if they die while the policy is active, a benefit is paid."&lt;SEP&gt;"The individual whose life is covered by the policy; the policy's benefits are triggered by their death."&lt;SEP&gt;"The individual whose life is covered by the policy; the trustee gains entitlement only after this person's death."&lt;SEP&gt;"The individual whose life is covered under the policy and who may become eligible for the waiver of premiums benefit."&lt;SEP&gt;"The individual whose life or health is covered under the policy, and whose death triggers potential benefit payments."&lt;SEP&gt;"The insured person is the individual covered by the policy who may become totally disabled and qualify for premium waiver."&lt;SEP&gt;"The insured person is the individual covered by the policy, who can renew coverage until age 80."&lt;SEP&gt;"The insured person is the individual whose life is covered under the insurance policy."&lt;SEP&gt;"The insured person is the individual whose life is covered under the policy, and may not be the policy owner."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-d797d61d4936328367b970f1b1a2a94b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-32b292e542e11e187b7d8150c2a86ba7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b8865028ed52b3b23f75c2db4581d310&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9e48b2c7f5c340d231cab1e863dc3229&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6e3c19fad0ec74d4024195693875376d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e336bc3335eae1b8a9a02061f363f289&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8671bd5f2e04dc9f4cc083e33b5d5daf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-03736d1fd2c6f92ba7855518c6ef9999&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cb04334968af2cf23772b1234fa1ff3c</data>
