<node id="&quot;PREMIUMS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"FINANCIAL CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Fixed payments for each 20-year term, guaranteed not to increase at renewal, regardless of age or health."&lt;SEP&gt;"Payments required to maintain the policy."&lt;SEP&gt;"Premiums are payments required under the insurance policy. The policy waives monthly premiums for the insured person during total disability, up to age 80."&lt;SEP&gt;"Premiums are the payments made to maintain the insurance policy."&lt;SEP&gt;"Premiums for TD 20-year Term Life insurance are fixed for each 20-year term and guaranteed not to increase during that term."&lt;SEP&gt;"Premiums for the converted permanent policy depend on the type and amount of coverage selected."&lt;SEP&gt;"Premiums for the waiver of premiums benefit are payable until the insured person reaches 65 years of age."&lt;SEP&gt;"Premiums may be affected by health changes, but in this case, they are guaranteed."&lt;SEP&gt;"The periodic payments required to maintain the policy, guaranteed not to increase during the policy term."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-7c9b2d4d50f1eb65ffb1c24f16aaff10&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d797d61d4936328367b970f1b1a2a94b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-32b292e542e11e187b7d8150c2a86ba7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6e3c19fad0ec74d4024195693875376d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e336bc3335eae1b8a9a02061f363f289&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9664b19d2f37c02c2b9b34d8418fd48b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8671bd5f2e04dc9f4cc083e33b5d5daf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d74a69ffda2d0b7001588e51837113ef</data>
