<edge source="&lt;hyperedge&gt;&quot;When you claim the Living benefit, you agree to the following conditions and limitations on your rights as a policy owner: - You may not cancel this policy; - If premiums are not paid, either directly or through the waiver benefit, the amount of any unpaid premiums will increase the amount of the living benefit. The living benefit amount and any unpaid premium amount will accumulate interest until the death of the insured person. Interest is set at the current prime rate and may be adjusted if prime fluctuates by 1% or more.&quot;" target="&quot;CANCELLATION RESTRICTION&quot;">
  <data key="d5">90.0</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-9e48b2c7f5c340d231cab1e863dc3229</data>
